external_knowledge:
- It is assumed that the user_id in the team_members table refers to the passenger_id in the passengers table; 
- The age rank is used as a proxy for ordering passengers from oldest to youngest within each class; 
- The Survival Analysis Team and Historical Data Team are specific teams within the research teams.

sql:
SELECT name
FROM passengers
ORDER BY name;

SELECT passenger_class, survival_rate
FROM survival_statistics
ORDER BY passenger_class ASC, survival_rate DESC;
